><br />\n知道我係邊個嘅話麻煩手下留情，thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦，借過嘅錢就一定要真金白銀還<br />\n我唔鐘意政府，但呢啲係納稅人比嘅錢嚟<br />\n所以我點都會還晒佢"},{"pid":"f09c1b447e1fe5188e6ab78940378a6d2d94ff6e","tid":1369901,"uid":54181,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec2527a0a863f3e051bf555e996e2a6321225e2b","tid":1369901,"uid":131120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96110c1233d95dd0553649758ddc4ddb1cc72fa6","tid":1369901,"uid":145558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦嫁大佬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbf88850cfe52851467eb13610895bfab67e0ea","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b5a80f2f8e190aedad7b4a230c990325ea90a6","tid":1369901,"uid":82332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490cb8c9c11731acbe63c86ff61bee3f4b807fd","tid":1369901,"uid":75046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"後門入番u都唔易 珍惜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46990b2a7784ef952bd01bc32b6f86e5c0b6dccd","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e0bc3dcf99dca8414beb849ab372f3e6949fc8","tid":1369901,"uid":53876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"嫁大陸佬共享支那榮耀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f3de583aa7278a33a6151c5e19d0bd5d492e4a","tid":1369901,"uid":105051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3bbf88850cfe52851467eb13610895bfab67e0ea","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b5a80f2f8e190aedad7b4a230c990325ea90a6","tid":1369901,"uid":82332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"加油，天無絕人之路，前面係點無人知。但你一定要完成degree. 我以前讀asso, 連ugc 都升唔返，就係掛住返pt, 賺嘅錢唔多，但後來升唔返ugc, 讀self fin 又負擔唔起，就出咗嚟做野。一開始收入好低，到而家都叫ok, 但途中為咗拎返個degree洗咗十幾萬，所以真係唔好放棄學業。<br />\n<br />\n二，你家庭情況唔好諗到咁壞，其實社福界有好多資源，有心社工，但你要主動求助，你唔好攬晒上身。<br />\n<br />\n三，感情，以我經驗，未到25歲唔好諗結婚住，雖然你已經成年，但你嘅人生閱歷尚淺，你同你男友可以傾下自己嘅想法。無論諗法係點，記得記得要講出嚟，愛情唔係妥協，唔係屈服，唔係成全。"},{"pid":"bb881e37fe4699b11b175d88e8dbbd000db00943","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d657d86f0ab12d7f98eb277b1bdcf816cb0801a","tid":1369901,"uid":216745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"一心帶埋你屋企人跟你男友返大陸算啦，一係係香港搵個有能力照顧到你地一家既"},{"pid":"95c5ee124fc9c0ec19115d8918c259e85261784e","tid":1369901,"uid":108016,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"小心條大陸仔呃香港身分證"},{"pid":"080a99d574bb8115313282467a960fb9abb195ea","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c5ee124fc9c0ec19115d8918c259e85261784e","tid":1369901,"uid":108016,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"小心條大陸仔呃香港身分證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"我都怕 所以我會睇定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你"},{"pid":"3bfd3391fac8113456fb5940101843c6f7f97b6f","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d657d86f0ab12d7f98eb277b1bdcf816cb0801a","tid":1369901,"uid":216745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"一心帶埋你屋企人跟你男友返大陸算啦，一係係香港搵個有能力照顧到你地一家既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問唔靚無學識又一陣窮人味，可能一世都搵唔到可以照顧埋我屋企嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都會慢慢觀察再選擇分唔分手，始終我屋企人上到去都係我照顧，倒不如留係香港做老姑婆，多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a033bbd2063ab1bcf6a1439256f8d19e1e7ec743","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"更正返，佢係住二線城市，不過都唔係你地口中所講嘅有錢仔，佢一家三口都要出去搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1456a752711f2d0f55ec5b0abdb2b24e8177cf","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f3de583aa7278a33a6151c5e19d0bd5d492e4a","tid":1369901,"uid":105051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3bbf88850cfe52851467eb13610895bfab67e0ea","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b5a80f2f8e190aedad7b4a230c990325ea90a6","tid":1369901,"uid":82332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"加油，天無絕人之路，前面係點無人知。但你一定要完成degree. 我以前讀asso, 連ugc 都升唔返，就係掛住返pt, 賺嘅錢唔多，但後來升唔返ugc, 讀self fin 又負擔唔起，就出咗嚟做野。一開始收入好低，到而家都叫ok, 但途中為咗拎返個degree洗咗十幾萬，所以真係唔好放棄學業。<br />\n<br />\n二，你家庭情況唔好諗到咁壞，其實社福界有好多資源，有心社工，但你要主動求助，你唔好攬晒上身。<br />\n<br />\n三，感情，以我經驗，未到25歲唔好諗結婚住，雖然你已經成年，但你嘅人生閱歷尚淺，你同你男友可以傾下自己嘅想法。無論諗法係點，記得記得要講出嚟，愛情唔係妥協，唔係屈服，唔係成全。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"其實真係想減輕還loans嘅壓力，但係咪唔建議返學期間返pt，最好都係summer break返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好怕到時我媽走咗我唔識分配好時間同錢去照顧我個妹，我唔食佢都要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過希望情況唔會真係咁快就變得咁壞<br />\n我有同男朋友講我覺得太快，我希望30歲左右先諗，佢開頭都話好，但係我呢兩日情緒真係唔穩定係咁同佢呻，佢就開始覺得自己等唔到咁耐，不過都係隨緣啦，可能好快就分手然后搵到個接受我背景嘅香港人，老實講我始終都係想嫁香港人，我對大陸人同大陸都會有偏見，但係暫時嚟講我個心得佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26933eca3d57013380009f4276785fe66a6a364b","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8490cb8c9c11731acbe63c86ff61bee3f4b807fd","tid":1369901,"uid":75046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"後門入番u都唔易 珍惜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"知道了，多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係好怕grad唔到"},{"pid":"4b4a1fd84c06270d777cd3c5a2ed382bc7413d82","tid":1369901,"uid":72228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"21歲就應該享受ulife<br />\n咁辛苦先駁翻上去<br />\n再者21歲咪咁撚快lock死自己option<br />\n咁早結婚自己都後悔<br />\n有時拍拖都要諗下自己"},{"pid":"eb08d272fe6414c7b718553c01e7798529fd83f0","tid":1369901,"uid":141452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b4a1fd84c06270d777cd3c5a2ed382bc7413d82","tid":1369901,"uid":72228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"21歲就應該享受ulife<br />\n咁辛苦先駁翻上去<br />\n再者21歲咪咁撚快lock死自己option<br />\n咁早結婚自己都後悔<br />\n有時拍拖都要諗下自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會嘗試多啲諗自己啦，我而家都覺得自己咁快決定結婚好唔理智同對我屋企人好不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c